name: British Informatics Olympiad Solutions
tagline: A collection of solutions to the British Informatics Olympiad questions
body:
### British Informatics Olympiad Solutions

In this repository, you will find solutions to various BIO questions from over the years, and the numbers will increase as I do them. They are all written in python, however if I decide at some point to do them in different languages, I will branch off from the master and put that in another branch.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
